ISLAMABAD, Oct 3 (APP):Caretaker Minister for Energy Muhammad Ali on Monday held a meeting with officials of Kuwait Foreign Petroleum Exploration Company (KUFPEC) on the sidelines of Abu Dhabi International Exhibition and Conference ADIPEC 23.
Both the sides discussed cooperation in exploration of opportunities, international ventures and human resource development, said a press release issued here.
